text: Why do you look so sad today?
Can’t you smile a little?
Sorry, but I’ve had a hard day.
This morning when I woke up, I-
If you would go to bed a little earlier
then you would feel happier.
Well, this morning when I woke up I-
I also find that exercising in the morning
makes me have a better day.
I agree, but this morning when I woke up I–
Oh, what did you eat for breakfast?
Eating a healthy breakfast
will definitely help you have a good day.
I did have a healthy breakfast,
but this morning when I woke up –
If you did all the things I suggested,
then you should be feeling good.
I don’t know why you're not.
Proverbs says,
Fools are not interested in understanding;
they only want to tell their own opinions.
